dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Douglas Diaz. May I have your name, please?
Hi Douglas, my name is Denise Mitchell.
Nice to meet you, Denise. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's zero zero two three four five.
Thank you, Denise. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle for verification purposes?
Of course, it's a two zero one eight Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you need assistance with regarding your policy today, Denise?
I'd like to inquire about adding roadside assistance to my coverage.
Absolutely, Denise. I can help you with that. Thank you for considering Old Stone Auto Insurance for your needs.
Thank you for your time, Denise. Have a wonderful day!
Thank you for your time, Denise. Have a wonderful day!
